<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td>
	     <table class="mform"  border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="0" width="100%" >
	     <form action="/cgi-bin/mrate.pl" name="f99002017738012">
	     <tr><td id="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top"><a id="sj" href="/db/item.html?item=1013&amp;mid=99002017738012">RE: Maax</a> <a id="fs8" href="/db/item.html?item=1013&amp;mid=99002017738012#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." width="17" height="11" /></a>
	     <br clear="all" /><small>Posted @ Wed, May 16th 9:36 AM 2001</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=23519"><span id=" ">Khaarq</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">15 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score:</span> Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>There's 2 mini-quests to complete the Screaming Mace quest.<br/><br/>Mini-quest #1: Kill Emperor Crush and loot his Dwarven Ringmail Tunic (DRT).&nbsp;&nbsp;Hail the Dwarven Smith in the slave camp and tell him "The king is dead", and ask about "ringmail".  He will ask you for the DRT. Give the DRT to the Dwarven Smith to receive the Dwarven Mace (DM).<br/><br/>Mini-quest #2: Kill the Orc Warlord and loot his Bracers of Battle (BoB). [You only need 1.  The name is plural for some reason]  Hail the High Elf Priest in the slave camp and tell him "The king is dead".  He will ask you for proof.  Give him the BoB to receive the Prayer Cloth of Tunare (PCoT).<br/><br/>Screaming Mace Quest: Give the High Elf Priest in the slave camp the DM and PCoT to receive your Screaming Mace.<br/></p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br />Khaarq</td></tr>
